percent against the U.S. dollar since July 2, has further added to
the cost of production and made it very difficult for the Commerce
Ministry to control consumer goods prices, Commerce Minister
Narongchai Akrasanee was quoted as saying on
Wednesday. (Thailand-Price Rises-Pressure)
