<HEADLINE> International Investment Fair Planned </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WUHAN, October 23 (Xinhua) -- An international trade fair
focused on investing in central and western China is scheduled for
November 18-23 in Wuhan, capital of Hubei Province.
</P>
