small-and-medium-sized enterprises in Latin America and the
Caribbean.
</P>
<P>
The multisector, global credit program, helping to finance a
broad range of business activities, will be carried out by the
Inter-American Investment Corporation (IIC), an affiliate of the
IDB that provides investments and credit to the private sector,
with emphasis on small-and medium-sized firms.
</P>
