<HEADLINE> Ramaala Takes Title of Race History </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BELGRADE, October 22 (Xinhua) -- Hendrick Ramaala of South
Africa surged ahead in a final sprint to beat from Kenyan Paul
Tergat to win the Belgrade Race Through History here on Wednesday.
</P>
